问题: $\left(x-\frac{1}{7 x}\right)^{7}$ 的展开式的第 2 项为

\[

\text{二项式定理:}

(a+b)^n=\sum_{k=0}^n C(n,k)a^{n-k}b^k=C(n,0)a^n+C(n,1)a^{n-1}b+\cdots +C(n,n)b^n.

\]

\[

\text{其中:}

C(n,k)=\frac{n!}{k!(n-k)!}.

\]

\[

\text{题目解析:

利用二项式定理, 可得:

\left(x-\frac{1}{7 x}\right)^{7}=\sum_{k=0}^{7} C(7,k)x^{7-k}\left(-\frac{1}{7 x}\right)^{k}

=C(7,0)x^{7}\left(-\frac{1}{7 x}\right)^{0}+C(7,1)x^{7-1}\left(-\frac{1}{7 x}\right)^{1}+\cdots +C(7,7)\left(-\frac{1}{7 x}\right)^{7}

=x^{7}+\left(-\frac{1}{7}\right)C(7,1)x^{6}\left(\frac{1}{x}\right)^{1}+\cdots +\left(-\frac{1}{7}\right)^{7}C(7,7)\left(\frac{1}{x}\right)^{7}

=x^{7}-\frac{1}{7}C(7,1)x^{5}+\cdots +\left(-\frac{1}{7}\right)^{7}C(7,7)\left(\frac{1}{x}\right)^{7}

\]

\[

\text{因此:}

\left(x-\frac{1}{7 x}\right)^{7} 的展开式的第 2 项为:

-\frac{1}{7}C(7,1)x^{5}=-\frac{1}{7}\cdot \frac{7!}{1!\cdot 6!}x^{5}=-7x^{5}.

\]

最终答案: $-7x^{5}$

